{"tid":2005500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"放寬限聚令前夕失守！港今增5確診 1宗經瑪麗檢測","createTime":"2020-05-07T06:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T07:45:42.000Z","uid":34251,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4b39b89ca044673a15a785c9d03f8997e4eb6c5c","tid":2005500,"uid":34251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:46:55.000Z","msg":"隨着本港武漢肺炎疫情稍緩和，政府多項禁令如限聚令等控制疫情措施周五凌晨將放寬，但據悉本港今日新增5宗武漢肺炎確診個案，包括4宗個案是海外回港人士無病徵個案，另一宗患者經瑪麗醫院檢測個案，是連續兩日出現本地及輸入個案零確診後，再有確診個案。衞生防護中心將於4時30分召開記者會交代詳情。《蘋果》將直播情況。<br />\n<br />\nsource 蘋果"},{"pid":"15a610481e12c488c3903a198b2c6713976ae842","tid":2005500,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:49:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鞭佢老母屍"},{"pid":"e409967da19524e87ca59f1abc8cd97e3844314b","tid":2005500,"uid":34251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd14323faa53b0710bca6cd7da98166a22233794","tid":2005500,"uid":36248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:50:43.000Z","msg":"Siu撚4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64186d1c66e2123211b7a5fdd568263c972bd62b","tid":2005500,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:50:44.000Z","msg":"係咪本地先"},{"pid":"c8d3f73de712ce8537d9aa06ccd4daef612c26fc","tid":2005500,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:53:18.000Z","msg":"特登報出黎"},{"pid":"576368a0a941a25350cdeaee078f0b44f7dc0422","tid":2005500,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T07:45:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">希望政府唔好因為咁小的反彈而取消放寬限聚令<br />\n如果唔係又要繼續無得做gym、睇戲、去酒吧、多於4人聚餐等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>